{"tid":1817283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入]呢隻蟲叫咩名同點隊冧","createTime":"2020-01-09T03:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T04:47:19.000Z","uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e67de2e56fe5f78535afb0e293b1a9539b4df2b","tid":1817283,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"上年先發現呢隻野<br />\n一開始得幾隻我都已經見隻拍隻 點知越拍越多 後來細佬成間房都係 仲開始進化到識吸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身都唔記得咗佢 因為上年一到秋冬天就突然消失哂<br />\n到今朝起身突然見番佢地就知春天要來 大鑊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇bus知佢叫咩名同點隊冧佢地 因為過兩日有隻貓bb會黎 唔想佢比人咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該哂咁多位bus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xWvOgd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxWvOgd9.jpg&h=de806648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVjO0FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVjO0FQ.jpg&h=b1fda847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sm84y0R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSm84y0R.jpg&h=fef302e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpXAFFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdpXAFFS.jpg&h=b20fdbfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sL4fFFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsL4fFFS.jpg&h=ae4ca259&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"078226a5124603400b6737b2886f5fa2bc77f25c","tid":1817283,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"最尾張圖唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor